(<i> sighs</i> )

18:22.709 --> 18:26.542
even need to explain

18:22.709 --> 18:26.542
an accident like this.

18:26.583 --> 18:29.417
Sometimes there just aren't

18:26.583 --> 18:29.417
any explanations.

