Lu-lu-lu-lu-lu.

19:29.834 --> 19:31.417
Lu-lu.

19:35.750 --> 19:40.250
You are still wearing

19:35.750 --> 19:40.250
that uniform. Why?

19:40.291 --> 19:41.750
I am a Starfleet officer.

19:41.792 --> 19:45.458
You are not

19:41.792 --> 19:45.458
<i>in</i> Starfleet any longer.

19:45.500 --> 19:48.083
It's time you adjusted

19:45.500 --> 19:48.083
your program to accept reality.

