I have been designed

19:58.667 --> 20:01.458
with a fundamental respect for

19:58.667 --> 20:01.458
life in all its forms

20:01.500 --> 20:04.792
and a strong inhibition against

20:01.500 --> 20:04.792
causing harm to living beings.

20:04.834 --> 20:06.542
What a marvelous

20:04.834 --> 20:06.542
contradiction--

20:06.583 --> 20:08.250
a military pacifist.

20:08.291 --> 20:10.583
Tell me, whose

20:08.291 --> 20:10.583
dreadful idea was it

20:10.625 --> 20:14.166
to enlist you in Starfleet

20:10.625 --> 20:14.166
to begin with?

20:14.208 --> 20:15.875
My skills seemed appropriate

20:14.208 --> 20:15.875
to...

20:15.917 --> 20:18.875
Data, Data, Data,

20:15.917 --> 20:18.875
big mistake, grievous error.

20:18.917 --> 20:20.333
You belong in Starfleet

20:20.375 --> 20:25.959
about as much as I belong

20:20.375 --> 20:25.959
in a verbal contract.

20:26.000 --> 20:27.917
Tell me, Data,

20:26.000 --> 20:27.917
have you killed yet?

20:27.959 --> 20:30.208
No, but I am programmed

20:30.250 --> 20:34.709
with the ability to use deadly

20:30.250 --> 20:34.709
force in the cause of defense.

20:34.750 --> 20:36.667
Shame on you.

20:36.709 --> 20:38.083
Shame on you.

20:38.125 --> 20:40.875
How neatly you rationalize

20:38.125 --> 20:40.875
your capabilities.

20:40.917 --> 20:44.500
How can you just casually

20:40.917 --> 20:44.500
accept your role in murder?

20:44.542 --> 20:46.250
I would not participate

20:44.542 --> 20:46.250
in a murder.

20:46.291 --> 20:48.000
Perhaps you misunderstand.

20:48.041 --> 20:51.834
Can't you see how much better

20:48.041 --> 20:51.834
it would be for you right here?

20:51.875 --> 20:54.083
The intellectual rewards

20:51.875 --> 20:54.083
alone...

20:54.125 --> 20:56.959
our personal exploration

20:54.125 --> 20:56.959
of the galaxy.

20:57.000 --> 21:00.709
I am at war with no one.

21:00.750 --> 21:03.000
I'm your liberator.

21:03.041 --> 21:05.250
You are a fine debater, sir.

21:05.291 --> 21:06.959
It is a pity you have used

21:05.291 --> 21:06.959
your verbal skills

21:07.000 --> 21:08.375
for mere hucksterism

21:08.417 --> 21:10.792
and the advancement

21:08.417 --> 21:10.792
of your own greed.

21:10.834 --> 21:13.875
Perhaps...

21:13.917 --> 21:15.792
perhaps you would not judge me

21:13.917 --> 21:15.792
so harshly

21:15.834 --> 21:19.500
if you knew

21:15.834 --> 21:19.500
of my desperate youth wasted...

21:19.542 --> 21:23.000
wasted on the streets

21:19.542 --> 21:23.000
of Zibalia.

21:23.041 --> 21:26.542
Your past does not excuse

21:23.041 --> 21:26.542
unethical or immoral

21:23.041 --> 21:26.542
behavior, sir.

21:26.583 --> 21:28.208
No it doesn't matter,

21:26.583 --> 21:28.208
it isn't true anyway.

21:28.250 --> 21:29.792
My father was quite wealthy,

21:28.250 --> 21:29.792
actually.

21:29.834 --> 21:32.500
He was a thief.

21:32.542 --> 21:36.000
Data, why don't you put on

21:32.542 --> 21:36.000
these lovely new clothes

21:36.041 --> 21:37.041
and go sit on the chair.

21:37.083 --> 21:39.125
I must decline.

21:39.166 --> 21:41.875
You're going to be

21:39.166 --> 21:41.875
much more of a challenge

21:41.917 --> 21:44.125
than I had first thought.

21:47.542 --> 21:50.583
Finoplak. 100 denkirs.

21:53.041 --> 21:59.834
Now, Data, in the meantime,

21:53.041 --> 21:59.834
here is something

21:59.875 --> 22:03.542
for your logic circuits

21:59.875 --> 22:03.542
to analyze.

