Personally, I'd be

22:17.959 --> 22:20.709
delighted to see you

22:17.959 --> 22:20.709
go around naked.

22:20.750 --> 22:24.125
I assume you have no modesty.

22:24.166 --> 22:30.750
But then, I guess

22:24.166 --> 22:30.750
that decency is the rule

22:30.792 --> 22:33.709
of your

22:30.792 --> 22:33.709
Starfleet training.

22:33.750 --> 22:36.583
In any case, Data

22:36.625 --> 22:38.166
why don't you

22:36.625 --> 22:38.166
make a decision

22:38.208 --> 22:42.625
about which alternative

22:38.208 --> 22:42.625
you dislike the least.

22:42.667 --> 22:44.333
Make a decision

22:42.667 --> 22:44.333
by dinnertime tonight.

22:44.375 --> 22:46.208
I've invited

22:44.375 --> 22:46.208
a guest to meet you.

22:46.250 --> 22:48.166
And I expect you to be

22:46.250 --> 22:48.166
as entertaining with him

22:48.208 --> 22:51.458
as you have been with me.

