<i>Enterprise,</i> shuttle bay two,

23:12.000 --> 23:15.500
prepare for docking.

23:15.542 --> 23:16.667
Level one precautions

23:16.709 --> 23:18.625
remain in effect.

23:24.500 --> 23:27.083
I did miss something.

23:40.959 --> 23:44.500
Your first watch at ops?

23:44.542 --> 23:47.709
I have served at

23:44.542 --> 23:47.709
the position before.

23:47.750 --> 23:50.834
I've been concerned

23:47.750 --> 23:50.834
about you.

23:50.875 --> 23:52.291
About me? Why?

23:52.333 --> 23:54.542
Because I know

23:52.333 --> 23:54.542
how I'd feel

23:54.583 --> 23:58.041
if I was asked to replace

23:54.583 --> 23:58.041
Data at his station.

24:02.083 --> 24:03.625
Bridge.

