I know, but this

24:13.417 --> 24:16.709
isn't the Klingon ship

24:16.750 --> 24:20.709
and Data was your friend,

24:16.750 --> 24:20.709
and it's the second time

24:20.750 --> 24:25.375
you've replaced

24:20.750 --> 24:25.375
a crew mate who's died.

