I honor Data's memory

24:25.417 --> 24:28.417
as I did Lieutenant Yar's

24:28.458 --> 24:30.333
by attempting

24:28.458 --> 24:30.333
to perform their duties

24:30.375 --> 24:32.792
as well as they did.

