Without communicating it?

26:07.333 --> 26:09.333
That doesn't sound like Data,

26:07.333 --> 26:09.333
either.

26:09.375 --> 26:13.792
Which means that maybe

26:09.375 --> 26:13.792
something was wrong with<i> him</i>

