I'm having a delightful visit.

28:18.333 --> 28:20.709
Come along,

28:18.333 --> 28:20.709
Varria.

28:20.750 --> 28:21.834
You're much

28:20.750 --> 28:21.834
more fun

28:21.875 --> 28:24.625
